# Boardroom minute drafts

Draft minutes generated by `scripts/provision-tenant.ts` (Wave 4 B-2) land here.

A human reviews each draft, then PRs it into
`8gi-foundation/8gi-governance/docs/boardroom-minutes/`. This directory is the
**staging area only**, not the canonical location.

Files in this directory are git-tracked: drafts that ship with a tenant should
be committed alongside the provisioning PR so the audit trail survives.
